{
  "text": "From the detection of the disease in citrus plants in America in 2004, research works on the biology of Diaphorina citri, the disease vector, have increased (Halbert and Manjunath, 2004; [CITATION_1] . [CITATION_2] stated that climate exerts a number of direct effects on the life cycle and reproduction of D. citri.",
  "correct_citation": {
